/resource/Ugo_Humbert\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The first-round men's doubles matches will be played on Saturday, July 27 and Sunday, July 28 - and like the singles - they will take place from 11am or 6pm UK time.\", \"from\": 1797, \"to\": 1962, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1954, \"end\": 1956, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9796899398655641, \"rank\": 0.020731109684421566, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Men's Singles: Cameron Norrie, Jack Draper, Dan Evans  Women's Singles: Katie Boulter  Men's Doubles: Joe Salisbury & Neal Skupski, Dan Evans & Andy Murray  Women's Doubles: Katie Boulter & Heather Watson  Mixed Doubles:Joe Salisbury & Heather Watson  It is almost certain Rafael Nadal is playing at the Olympics for the last time before his retirement from professional men's tennis - if he does not withdraw due to hisworrying new thigh injury.\", \"from\": 1964, \"to\": 2410, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1979, \"end\": 1993, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cameron_Norrie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cameron Norrie\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cameron_Norrie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cameron_Norrie\"}, {\"begin\": 1995, \"end\": 2006, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Draper_(tennis)\", \"score\": 0.9926967693033829, \"rank\": 0.007352941176469691, \"text\": \"Jack Draper\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Draper_(tennis)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Draper_(tennis)\"}, {\"begin\": 2237, \"end\": 2249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rafael Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \